headline: Synopsys Pops as Chip Export Restrictions Lift. Should You Buy SNPS Stock Now?
summary: Synopsys shares gained after the White House lifted restrictions on export of chip-design software to China. Berenberg analysts believe SNPS shares could hit $600 in the coming months.
